author: @VyMauricio
text:
SungTaro are adorable enough but we also get to see them interact with animals, found myself smiling from ear to ear with this content! 💚

Kinda amusing how Shotaro’s hair is styled like an alpaca. Shotaro naming animals is really a thing. A bit unfortunate that Shotaro’s SHOrt Trip, where he named the sheep Machiko, was only featured in the NCT JP Twitter account (and without subs). I’m not sure if many people know about it. It’s also so cute how he was talking to the alpacas in Japanese like “hai”, “dozo”, and calling them “-chan”, he was super excited. He also could not get enough of the dogs! I can see how much he wanted to rub his face on Saehae. I wonder if he remembers Choco. He was also really nice to share the little girl some of his treats to feed the alpacas.

Sungchan being scared of the alpacas kinda reminded me of Jisung, giant maknaes who get scared sometimes. His MC skills really came out and he led this content really well.
